8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Coda AI and Smartsheet share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Collaboration, Automation. Where Coda AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Notes, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Smartsheet uniquely offers Calendar, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Coda AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Smartsheet scores 7/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Coda AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Smartsheet's starting price of $9/mo. Coda AI has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Smartsheet does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
